snippet.title: Icarus Proudbottom's Typing Party - Itch.io Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Icarus Proudbottom's Typing Party is the world's first local multiplayer typing party game!
Plug two keyboards into one computer and you're ready to party!

Download it on itch.io here here: https://holywow.itch.io/typingparty

This is a multiplayer game at heart and is designed to be played with friends - however, you can practice the game single-player by competing against Mark 22, a computer controlled opponent!

FEATURES:
- Face off with NINE amazing minigames!
- Practice against the computer in single-player mode!
- Two versions of the game are included: the standard version, plus the "ARCADE VERSION" - a simpler, shorter version that doesn't require a mouse and can be set up as an installation.
